# Profile: local, vendor-free extraction via Ollama. Embedder stays Gemini (no reindex).
#
# BEST-EFFORT depending on your image: some standalone images force the OpenAI Responses API for
# provider=openai, which Ollama (Chat Completions) does not speak -> 404. Verify first, or route
# via an OpenAI-compatible gateway (e.g. LiteLLM). See docs/DEPLOY.md.
#
# Requires on the Ollama host: `OLLAMA_HOST=0.0.0.0:11434` and reachability from the memory host
# (tailnet/LAN). Replace <ollama-host> with your Ollama machine's IP/hostname.
# OPENAI_API_KEY may be a dummy (e.g. "ollama") but must be set.
LLM_PROVIDER=openai
OPENAI_API_URL=http://<ollama-host>:11434/v1
MODEL_NAME=qwen2.5:14b
EMBEDDER_PROVIDER=gemini
EMBEDDER_MODEL=gemini-embedding-001
EMBEDDER_DIMENSIONS=768
SEMAPHORE_LIMIT=4
